    "name": "Split Souls",
    "steam_appid": 3313390,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313390/extras/c36aa5f5d76b69158128b3338078fd8b.avif?t=1760439934\" width=230 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313390/extras/2ad3440007ea44ae46f0d9b58e4a84ea.webp?t=1760439934\" width=252 height=55 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i>The Player's soul has been split into 2 and it's the job of the player to get the souls back together. </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">This game was made for an nice gamejam called: The Hyper Unicorn GameJam. With 3 themes to choose out, I choose bound together. I hope you like the game and have fun with it and don't forget to stay awesome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">If there's any bugs within the game or suggestions in the game, You can always send it within the reviews here down below, and I will try to apply it as soon as possible to make the experience much better for the player.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3313390/extras/e9993a576fb821c666ee102406b6ff95.avif?t=1760439934\" width=252 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Like any other platformers, you have the usual jumping, dashing and also hanging unto walls. But throughout the play sessions, you will also have other little things, like Gravity changing platforms, Automatic Jumping Platforms, Teleport Platforms and Shrinking Platforms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">The player also has to avoid other certain obstacles like spikes, lava, bullet pallets from turrets and even the Corrupt Souls. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Corrupted Souls are the souls that didn't make it, and had their souls not be set to one in time, or an part of their very soul died, and would make them corrupted. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p>",
